arStrings.szText:
Casting a {c_important}Focus{/c} Skill recalls all Nearby {c_important}{u}Storm Feathers{/u}{/c}, dealing {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1 * (1+Owner.Bonus_Percent_Per_Power#Spiritborn_Feather_Spawn)]{/c} Lightning damage to enemies along their way. 

If there are no Nearby {c_important}{u}Storm Feathers{/u}{/c}, the cast instead spawns {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} randomly around you.

Casting a {c_important}Focus{/c} Skill recalls all Nearby {c_important}{u}Storm Feathers{/u}{/c}, dealing {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1 * (1+Owner.Bonus_Percent_Per_Power#Spiritborn_Feather_Spawn)]{/c} Lightning damage to enemies along their way. 

If there are no Nearby {c_important}{u}Storm Feathers{/u}{/c}, the cast instead spawns {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} randomly around you.
